      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1088-1117",
      "markText": "革命数十年尚未成功的一个重要原因就是没有一支真正的革命军。",
      "totalCount": 182,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=31824849&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1088&rangeEnd=1117",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/16a3268071e59bd116afa0a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1088&rangeEnd=1117"
